Title: Event Sourcing and DDD Hand In Hand (Practical Refactoring)
Description:
Event Sourcing and DDD might fit very well together. I'd dare to say that DDD comes more natural to event sourced and event driven systems than to regular layered applications. In this video I start from some pre-existing code that uses event sourcing to model a business domain. But the code has some major drawbacks. During the video I'll go through some practical refactoring that shows how combining some tactical DDD patterns with event sourcing might result in a robust setup. That's why this video might be an excellent DDD and event sourcing tutorial.
